article.description: — Abu Kigab registered 18 points as Boise State beat UNLV 69-63 on Friday night.
article.headline: Kigab scores 18 to lift Boise State past UNLV 69-63
article.linkText: Kigab scores 18 to lift Boise State past UNLV 69-63
article.story: BOISE, Idaho -- — Abu Kigab registered 18 points as Boise State beat UNLV 69-63 on Friday night. Tyson Degenhart had 15 points and seven rebounds for Boise State (19-5, 10-1 Mountain West Conference). Marcus Shaver Jr. added 13 points and Mladen Armus had 12 points and seven rebounds. Bryce Hamilton had 32 points for the Runnin' Rebels (14-11, 6-6). Michael Nuga added 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
